name: Original Rebirth
description: Original Rebirth was created in 2012 in anticipation of becoming a Father. All of my hopes and fears were expressed through the creative process of which I did not plan and let the brushes take over. Through this process my subconscious mapped and planned the final piece that still holds true to all of my hopes & fears today 2021. While this piece is open to interpretation I find it to be a self portrait in a sense. High quality jpeg edition of 88
